&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;As a second-year student, what’s the one piece of advice you hear the most? Get your foot in the door with a company that can secure your professional future ASAP. It’s time to get your career started with Jumpstart at ALKU. Jumpstart is a 2-day educational program hosted at ALKU HQ in Andover, MA with the goal of educating and providing the first steps for an eventual exclusive internship within one of the fastest growing staffing firms in the nation. Bring the hunger to learn and grow, and we’ll provide the tools, support, and mentorship you need to succeed. Jumpstart at ALKU is the perfect opportunity for any second-year student looking to get started in sales, build up your resume, and meet professionals that you can stay connected with for the rest of your career. You’ll be sitting down with ALKU sales superstars prepared to cover all aspects, unveil crucial tips, and offer real-world advice regarding the sales and staffing industries.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Spend the day experiencing the energy of ALKU, networking with industry experts, and participating in educational sessions catered to career growth and engagement. The main goal of Jumpstart at ALKU is to ensure you walk away feeling completely confident and secure in your professional future. Think of it as your first big move toward an amazing career in sales — and the beginning of your ALKU story.&lt;/div&gt;
